    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, the rod bearings have been addressed, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh OEM bushings, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are known for. Documentation is exhaustive, confirming a life of meticulous preventative maintenance.",
